nodes.text: Jessica Tuck (born February 19, 1963) is an American actress who provides additional voices in the 2019 film Star Wars: Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker. She best known for her performances on television as Megan Gordon Harrison on the ABC soap opera One Life to Live, Gillian Gray in the CBS drama series Judging Amy, and as American Vampire League spokesperson Nan Flanagan on the HBO series True Blood.
